", "description": "Agent invocation config (wire to Agent.config)", "type": 5}, {"name": "abort", "description": "Abort signal (wire to Agent.abort)", "type": 6}], "color": "#626060"}, {"id": "tool", "name": "Tool", "description": "Define tools with arguments and results for AI agents", "svgIcon": "<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<svg width=\"1200pt\" height=\"1200pt\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 1200 1200\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n <path d=\"m869.16 737.63-137.95-137.95-59.953 59.953 19.031 19.031c18.609 18.516 26.156 45.938 19.641 71.531-5.6719 22.172-21.562 39.938-42.094 49.266l70.031 70.031c-15.797 61.031 0 128.68 47.906 176.29 51.844 52.078 127.08 66.281 192.1 43.172l-86.812-86.812c-17.109-17.109-17.109-44.484 0-61.594l50.016-50.016c17.109-17.109 44.484-17.109 61.594 0l86.812 86.812c22.922-65.016 8.6719-139.97-43.172-192.1-47.906-47.906-115.78-63.656-177.1-47.625z\"/>\n <path d=\"m330.84 462.37 69.75 69.75c9.3281-20.531 27.094-36.469 49.266-42.094 5.8594-1.5469 12.234-2.3438 18.562-2.3438 20.016 0 38.859 7.8281 53.016 22.078l18.984 18.984 59.953-59.953-138.24-138.24c15.797-61.031 0-128.68-47.906-176.53-51.844-51.844-127.08-66.047-191.81-42.891l86.578 86.578c17.109 17.109 17.109 44.484 0 61.594l-50.016 50.016c-17.109 17.109-44.484 17.109-61.594 0l-86.578-86.578c-23.156 64.734-8.9531 139.97 42.891 191.81 48.141 48.141 115.78 63.938 177.1 47.906z\"/>\n <path d=\"m1032.4 107.44-145.03 84.891-19.219 79.359-327.79 327.79-54.422-54.422c-6.2344-6.2344-15.234-8.8125-23.859-6.5625-8.5312 2.1562-15.281 8.7188-17.812 17.156l-19.688 66.797-66.797 19.688c-3.9844 1.1719-7.6406 3.3281-10.594 6.2812l-199.82 199.82c-27.281 27.281-42.281 63.562-42.281 102.14 0 38.578 15.047 74.859 42.281 102.14 27.281 27.281 63.562 42.281 102.14 42.281 38.578 0 74.859-15.047 102.14-42.281l199.82-199.82c2.9531-2.9531 5.1094-6.6094 6.2812-10.594l19.688-66.797 66.797-19.688c8.4375-2.4844 14.953-9.2344 17.156-17.812 2.1562-8.5312-0.28125-17.625-6.5625-23.859l-54.422-54.42